description:
Here's a big, muscular, southern boy. His name is Cedric, but he goes by "Rick."
He's 20 years old and this is his first time outside his home state of Alabama.
He broke up with his girlfriend a few weeks ago and he lives at home with his parents. Oddly enough, he claims that the ex-girlfriend AND his parents know what he's up to.
"I told them it was a lot of money," he said. "I was going out there. I didn't care."
I'm not sure if I believe him or not, because it's hard to imagine any parents from Alabama not having a shit fit over something like this.
Even so, I couldn't get over how cute his accent was and the fact that he seemed so happy to be here.
For a 20-year-old, he's got the biggest sets of quads I've ever seen. They're enormous!
"My pants fit real tight," he said. "The girls like it."
title: Cedric
